.SH "NAME"
AnyEvent::Impl::Perl \- AnyEvent adaptor for AnyEvent's pure perl AnyEvent::Loop
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 3
\&   use AnyEvent;
